WEBVTT

00:04:28.400 --> 00:04:34.256
So if you seek your happiness
only in control,

00:04:34.280 --> 00:04:38.920
you are only giving yourself
stress and unhappiness.

00:04:39.520 --> 00:04:44.416
It has often been seen

00:04:44.440 --> 00:04:51.440
that the more successful you
get the more control you seek.

00:04:52.920 --> 00:04:56.650
Maybe that is the reason why people

00:04:56.650 --> 00:05:01.560
who are successful are 
very often not really happy,